* Skapa regementen (på bestämd form, typ Reg#1?)
* Flytta regementen (efter reg-namn, flytta enbart i fyra/åtta-riktningar?)
* Fyll på/plocka bort trupper ur regementen
* Flytta trupper mellan regementen

* Querys över units?


Leonardo-example
------------------
CREATE [regname] AT [x, y]
CREATE GUNMAN [unitName]
-||-   SNIPER -||-
-||-   ARTILLERY -||-
-||-   MEDIC -||-
-||-   TANK -||-

ADD [unitName] TO [regname]
REMOVE [unitName] FROM [regname]
REMOVE NUMBER [index] OF [unitType] FROM [regname]  

TRANSFER [unitName] FROM [regname1] TO [regname2]
MOVE [regname] [y] STEPS [NORTH/SOUTH] AND [x] STEPS [EAST/WEST]

GET POSITION FOR [regname]
GET SIZE OF [regname]
GET AMOUNT OF [unitType] IN [regname]